 * This class creates the hex objects that will be used to make the grid. 
 * 
 * Its boolean values will determine if food, ants, rocks and hives will be placed...
 *...there. Needs revising, I think I'm tired. I can't figure out how I thought...
 *...this would work originally.
 * 
 * If you edit this, please comment what you have changed and re-upload it please.
 * ----------------------------------GROUP6----------------------------------
